tle=Kenyon Review for Literary Achievement|url=http://www.kenyonreview.org/programs/kenyon-review-award-for-literary-achievement/|website=KenyonReview.org}}</ref>\n* 2005 [[Irish PEN Award]]<ref>[http://www.irishpen.com/irish-pen-award-for-literature/ \"Irish PEN Award for Literature\"], [[Irish PEN]].</ref>\n* 2006 [[T. S. Eliot Prize]] for ''[[District and Circle]]''<ref name=\"times-obit\"/>\n* 2007 [[Poetry Now Award]] for ''District and Circle''<ref name=\"it2011\" /><ref>[http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/ireland/2007/0331/1175003571927.html Heaney work a unanimous choice] ''Irish Times'', 31 March 2007.</ref>\n* 2009 [[David Cohen Prize]]<ref name=\"times-obit\"/>\n* 2011 [[Poetry Now Award]] for ''[[Human Chain (poetry)|Human Chain]]''<ref name=\"it2011\">\"[http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/ireland/2011/0326/1224293135913.html Heaney wins 'Irish Times' poetry award]\", ''Irish Times'', 26 March 2011.</ref>\n* 2011 [[Irish Book Awards|Bob Hughes Lifetime Achievement Award]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/ireland/2011/1118/1224307765902.html |title=Heaney honoured at book awards |author=Ronan McGreevy |work=The Irish Times |date=18 November 2011 |accessdate=23 April 2019}}</ref>\n* 2012 [[Griffin Poetry Prize]], Lifetime Recognition Award<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/weekend/2012/0616/1224318011868.html|title=Heaney wins top Canadian prize|date=16 June 2012|accessdate=16 June 2012|first=Giles|last=Newington|work=The Irish Times|publisher=Irish Times Trust}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Poetry}}\n* [[List of Nobel laureates in Literature]]\n* [[List of people on stamps of Ireland]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Commons category}}\n* [http://www.nobel.se/literature/laureates/1995/heaney-lecture.html Heaney's Nobel acceptance speech]\n*{{Worldcat id|lccn-n79-99140}}\n*{{IMDb name|2573636}}\n* [http://www.poetryfoundation.org/bio/seamus-heaney Seamus Heaney] at the